---
title: BBQ Beef & Pork Meatballs with Chive Mixed Veggie Mash & Garden Salad
description: How many meatballs are too many? The answer is you can never have enough of these herb-infused beef and pork meatballs covered in our punchy BBQ sauce. A cauliflower and potato mash balances the whole dish out for you to enjoy until your appetite is content.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

*Unfortunately, this
week's tomato was in
